00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,980
= Episode 46 =

20
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:35,820
Princess.

21
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:38,300
His Majesty told me to send you

22
00:01:38,300 --> 00:01:39,260
some gadgets.

23
00:01:40,580 --> 00:01:41,460
Put them there.

24
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:52,380
Don’t you look a look?

25
00:01:52,820 --> 00:01:54,340
His Majesty specially...

26
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:55,100
No.

27
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:04,420
= Princess Huirou =

28
