to send you these.

32
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:16,740
He didn’t ask me to persuade you.

33
00:02:16,740 --> 00:02:17,460
You...

34
00:02:24,660 --> 00:02:25,540
How come you don’t leave?

35
00:02:26,460 --> 00:02:28,780
Because His Majesty told me

36
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:31,100
to check your homework.

37
00:02:33,220 --> 00:02:34,740
You wrote several words wrong

38
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,220
in Ouyang Xiu’s Notes on Zuiweng Pavilion.

39
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:38,780
You haven’t memorized Fan Zhongyan’s

40
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,100
Notes on Yueyang Pavilion.

41
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:42,060
Su Shunqin

42
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:43,860
wrote Notes on Canglang Pavilion lately.

43
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:45,820
His Majesty reads it over and over.

44
00:02:46,220 --> 00:02:46,940
He meant to...

45
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:48,860
They were all demoted.

46
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:50,260
Why didn’t they introspect themselves

47
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:51,180
at home

48
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:53,100
but happily travel around and have fun?

49
00:02:55,220 --> 00:02:56,100
They enjoyed themselves

50
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:57,380
but wrote

51
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:59,060
these long essays to annoy me.

52
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,340
Why didn’t father punish them

53
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:03,060
but punish me to memorize these?

54
00:03:13,140 --> 00:03:14,020
Father likes the essays

55
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:15,300
written by the talents so much,

56
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,340
and asks me to memorize so many.

57
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:22,780
Now he betroths me to Li Wei.

58
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,140
Will he also let him

59
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:26,380
write

60
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:27,780
such long notes thingy

61
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:29,260
to let me memorize?

62
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:32,980
Princess.

63
00:03:35,740 --> 00:03:37,860
Maybe when your mansion is built,

64
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:40,460
your bridegroom-to-be will

65
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:43,220
write an essay about Immortal Descending Pavilion.

66
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:46,620
Immortal Descending Pavilion?

67
00:03:48,380 --> 00:03:49,740
That’s a usual name.

68
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:54,860
Stop fooling me.

69
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:57,620
It’s said that Li Wei

70
00:03:58,980 --> 00:04:00,260
is neither good-looking

71
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:01,780
nor smart.

72
00:04:02,820 --> 00:04:04,420
He’s already 16,

73
00:04:04,980 --> 00:04:06,180
yet he just finishes the Book of Filial Piety.

74
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:08,820
There are tons of Confucius’s and Mencius’ books

75
00:04:08,820 --> 00:04:10,020
for him to learn.

76
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,540
He has no time to learn poetry at all.

77
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:14,180
How can he

78
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:16,260
write poems with me in the future?

79
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:21,940
Are you laughing

80
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,300
that my poems are bad?

81
00:04:24,620 --> 00:04:25,340
I dare not.

82
00:04:26,580 --> 00:04:28,860
You’re a master of poetry.

83
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:31,100
Obviously, you're laughing at me.

84
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:37,620
Perhaps

85
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:41,060
my poems are average indeed.

86
00:04:43,420 --> 00:04:44,580
But Cao

87
00:04:45,380 --> 00:04:47,300
is a master of poems for sure.

88
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:54,860
Did you ever write poems

89
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:55,820
together with Mr. Cao?

90
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:57,100
I didn’t.

91
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:02,580
I... I won’t show my shortcomings

92
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:03,420
in front of Cao.

93
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:08,700
How do you know Mr. Cao

94
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:09,700
is a master of poems?

95
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:12,460
He is good-looking

96
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:14,260
and so smart.

97
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:16,940
His acrobatics are outstanding as well.

98
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,940
I heard that he’s also a marksman.

99
00:05:20,540 --> 00:05:21,540
With his eyes blindfolded,

100
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,780
he can still shoot down flying geese.

101
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:29,100
He is like an immortal.

102
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:32,060
He must be adept at poems, isn’t he?

103
00:05:33,580 --> 00:05:35,660
I’m willing to go there.

104
00:05:36,780 --> 00:05:37,380
OK.

105
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:41,540
Wen Yanbo,

106
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:43,180
the Assistant Administrator,

107
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:44,220
is appointed as the Military Governor,

108
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:47,220
and the Left Adviser Ming Hao as the deputy

109
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:48,780
to eliminate the rebels in Beizhou City.

110
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:56,580
It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

111
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:01,580
The situation on the battlefield changes rapidly.

112
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:03,700
Mistake is inevitable for a messenger.

113
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:06,500
Wen Yanbo takes charge of the battlefield issues

114
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:07,420
and acts at your discretion.

115
00:06:13,700 --> 00:06:15,900
I have a family matter.

116
00:06:16,700 --> 00:06:18,140
I’d like to hear your advice.

117
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,900
After all, my family matters

118
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,500
are not personal.

119
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:37,820
That is to pick a bridegroom for Princess Fukang.

120
00:06:41,980 --> 00:06:43,900
= Chen Zhizhong, courtesy name Zhaoyu =
Princess Fukang is 14,

121
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:46,180
a proper age to pick a bridegroom for her.

122
00:06:46,660 --> 00:06:48,700
Your Majesty.

123
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,780
Do you have any candidates?

124
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:57,100
Li Wei,

125
00:06:58,300 --> 00:06:59,980
the second of son

126
00:07:00,300 --> 00:07:02,700
of my uncle Li Yonghe.

127
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:09,060
= Li Yonghe, courtesy name Shenli =

128
00:07:10,700 --> 00:07:14,300
-It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.
-It’s wise of you, Your Majesty.

129
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:33,660
Huaiji.

130
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,620
You know.

131
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:39,300
Since father will marry me to someone,

132
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:42,740
why doesn’t he marry me to Cao?

133
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:45,300
Father

134
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:46,700
doesn’t like Her Highness.

135
00:07:48,180 --> 00:07:49,860
That’s why he doesn’t like her family?

136
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,580
That’s His Majesty’s decision.

137
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:57,220
I dare not make comments.

138
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:03,660
Huaiji. I see you as my brother.

139
00:08:04,180 --> 00:08:05,620
Why do you fob me off with bureaucratic language

140
00:08:06,340 --> 00:08:07,740
like other eunuches?

141
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,180
Huaiji.

142
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:15,620
I don’t want to leave father, Her Highness, mother

143
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:17,620
and you.

144
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:29,060
But if it’s Cao,

145
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:31,700
that won’t be too bad.

146
00:08:33,380 --> 00:08:35,140
Cao is good-looking.

147
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:37,780
All girls would like him.

148
00:08:41,740 --> 00:08:46,020
Cao is also Her Highness’s nephew.

149
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:47,820
If I marry him,

150
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:50,100
it means I marry to Her Highness's family.

151
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:52,340
Her Highness’s family

152
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:54,420
must be kind to me.

153
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,140
But

154
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:01,140
Li Wei is His Majesty’s relative.

155
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:06,340
His Majesty must be worried

156
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:07,300
that you could suffer a lot

157
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:09,220
outside of the family.

158
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:11,140
Maybe

159
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:16,900
His Majesty doesn’t know very well

160
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:18,820
about Her Highness’s family.

161
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:22,780
His Majesty favors and trusts Li Yonghe

162
00:09:24,260 --> 00:09:25,260
the most,

163
00:09:26,180 --> 00:09:27,300
and is also very close to him.

164
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:29,940
So His Majesty believes

165
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:33,180
only you marry into Li’s family

166
00:09:34,180 --> 00:09:35,540
can you be loved and cared

167
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,940
like staying with His Majesty

168
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:42,540
and Madam Miao in the palace.

169
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:47,540
Really?

170
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:55,020
His Majesty loves you the most

171
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:57,900
in the world.

172
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:06,900
His Majesty’s filial piety

173
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:08,020
is well-praised.

174
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:10,020
Only because unaware of the truth,

175
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:12,340
Your Majesty failed to do filial duty
to Empress Dowager Zhangyi.

176
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:14,660
That’s Your Majesty’s unintentional mistake.

177
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:17,900
= He Tan, courtesy name Shengcong =
Princess Fukang is Your Majesty’s beloved daughter.

178
00:10:18,060 --> 00:10:20,460
If she’s betrothed to the Lis to comfort
Empress Dowager,

179
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:22,420
it can make up for the mistake.

180
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:24,940
In my opinion,

181
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:27,380
as Your Majesty’s intimate relative,

182
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,580
ranked among the ministers,

183
00:10:28,780 --> 00:10:30,620
Li Yonghe is thrifty, keeping away from power,

184
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:32,980
and having no private mansion in the Capital.

185
00:10:33,580 --> 00:10:35,900
If the princess can marry to the Lis,

186
00:10:36,060 --> 00:10:38,660
there will be no worry about their corruption.

187
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,940
Your Majesty offered mansions to him many times,

188
00:10:41,940 --> 00:10:43,020
but he rejected.

189
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:45,180
By the chance of the marriage,

190
00:10:45,660 --> 00:10:46,980
the Li’s family can be heavily rewarded.

191
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:48,900
It not only can

192
00:10:49,180 --> 00:10:50,780
have Empress Dowager rest in peace,

193
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:52,580
= Sima Guang, courtesy name Junshi =
but people can also be civilized.

194
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:54,260
Commoners will

195
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:55,860
be moved

196
00:10:55,980 --> 00:10:58,780
by His Majesty’s filial piety.

197
00:11:03,860 --> 00:11:05,820
Since you all agree,

198
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:07,660
I will determine

199
00:11:07,860 --> 00:11:09,700
Li Wei, Li Yonghe’s son,

200
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:10,980
to be my son-in-law,

201
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,860
the groom-to-be of Princess Fukang.

202
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:14,940
When the princess comes of age,

203
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:16,620
the wedding will be held.

204
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:22,340
This snack is so good.

205
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:24,100
There are always new snacks

206
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:25,380
outside.

207
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:27,180
But those in the palace

208
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:28,980
are still the old kinds years ago.

209
00:11:30,060 --> 00:11:31,780
His Majesty and Her Highness are frugal.

210
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:33,580
We dare not have

211
00:11:33,580 --> 00:11:35,260
delicate food or clothing in the palace.

212
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:37,820
We would be blamed for luxury

213
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:38,900
and extravagance.

214
00:11:39,140 --> 00:11:40,900
The world has been peaceful these years.

215
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:41,780
People live happily.

216
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:43,340
The wealthy families

217
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,300
are good at enjoying these.

218
00:11:44,460 --> 00:11:45,780
The food and amusements outside

219
00:11:45,780 --> 00:11:47,380
are upgraded fast.

220
00:11:51,060 --> 00:11:53,500
Mother. If I get married,

221
00:11:53,660 --> 00:11:55,060
can I go out to have fun?

222
00:11:55,460 --> 00:11:56,580
Can I go to the night market,

223
00:11:56,660 --> 00:11:57,780
watch shows in theater,

224
00:11:57,980 --> 00:11:59,380
and go to walk in the countryside?

225
00:12:00,780 --> 00:12:02,780
You’re still the princess even if you get married.

226
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:04,820
You can’t go to places

227
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:05,620
or do what you want

228
00:12:05,620 --> 00:12:06,300
as you please.

229
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:07,900
You are not a civilian girl.

230
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:14,300
However,

231
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:16,940
the rules are not as strict as in the palace.

232
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:19,300
If your husband

233
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:20,780
will accompany you,

234
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:23,140
it’s OK to hang out

235
00:12:23,340 --> 00:12:24,340
occasionally.

236
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:28,340
But mother,

237
00:12:30,340 --> 00:12:31,340
I heard that

238
00:12:31,780 --> 00:12:34,900
the groom-to-be doesn’t look good,

239
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:36,980
and he’s also stupid.

240
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:39,060
When others ask him questions,

241
00:12:39,620 --> 00:12:41,180
he answers very slowly.

242
00:12:44,500 --> 00:12:45,620
Even if such a husband

243
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:47,340
accompanies me to go out,

244
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:48,980
I won’t feel happy.

245
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:54,660
Fine.

246
00:12:56,980 --> 00:12:58,860
It is still a long time

247
00:12:58,860 --> 00:12:59,860
before you get married.

248
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:02,460
You’d better read

249
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:04,180
and memorize Notes on Canglang Pavilion

250
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:05,340
first.

251
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:07,300
You’ll be punished

252
00:13:07,860 --> 00:13:08,780
if you can’t answer

253
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:10,740
when your father comes back and asks you.

254
00:13:32,460 --> 00:13:33,180
Your Highness.

255
00:13:33,540 --> 00:13:35,540
Would you prefer to take

256
00:13:35,540 --> 00:13:36,780
the crown with beads?

257
00:13:38,220 --> 00:13:39,780
Are you preparing crowns

258
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:42,420
for the rest of my life

259
00:13:42,420 --> 00:13:43,420
before you leave the palace?

260
00:13:47,140 --> 00:13:47,900
Your Highness.

261
00:14:10,820 --> 00:14:13,620
You can leave the palace in ten days or so.

262
00:14:14,220 --> 00:14:15,900
You’ve expected it for tens of hundreds of days.

263
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:17,980
It will come true finally.

264
00:14:21,020 --> 00:14:23,420
Are you crying out of joy?

265
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:26,620
Your Highness.

266
00:14:27,060 --> 00:14:28,500
You know I’m not.

267
00:14:31,260 --> 00:14:32,140
I understand.

268
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:37,580
You care about me,

269
00:14:38,740 --> 00:14:39,740
and don’t want to leave me.

270
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:45,180
More than that,

271
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:51,460
you’re worried about me.

272
00:15:00,660 --> 00:15:02,540
I know you like

273
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:05,740
that set of my perfume tools.

274
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:08,220
It’s broken.

275
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:10,260
But I got

276
00:15:10,820 --> 00:15:12,820
two better sets for you.

277
00:15:19,620 --> 00:15:20,660
I didn’t see Ling’er today.

278
00:15:20,660 --> 00:15:21,900
Where is she?

279
00:15:23,540 --> 00:15:25,340
She caught a cold,

280
00:15:25,460 --> 00:15:26,620
and was afraid to get you infected.

281
00:15:27,020 --> 00:15:28,660
So, she doesn’t come on duty today.

282
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:32,380
Ling’er gets sick

283
00:15:32,500 --> 00:15:33,900
many times in the past months.

284
00:15:34,580 --> 00:15:35,660
Call a physician

285
00:15:35,660 --> 00:15:36,660
to treat her tomorrow.

286
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:49,900
Your Majesty.

287
00:15:50,340 --> 00:15:51,380
What are you looking for?

288
00:15:52,060 --> 00:15:52,980
Let me help you.

289
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:23,620
This was written by Her Highness

290
00:16:24,020 --> 00:16:24,980
many years ago.

291
00:16:25,660 --> 00:16:27,140
She meant to ask you for advice.

292
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:31,660
Huan was still here back then.

293
00:16:32,740 --> 00:16:33,580
She said

294
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:35,900
it’s a personal letter

295
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:37,740
from Her Highness to you.

296
00:16:50,420 --> 00:16:52,020
These painting tools are also for you.

297
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:56,060
And a jar of wine Peach Blossom.

298
00:16:56,580 --> 00:16:57,780
I studied a long time

299
00:16:57,980 --> 00:16:59,060
and made it specially for you

300
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:03,860
I won’t be able go to your wedding.

301
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:05,820
On the day you get married,

302
00:17:06,100 --> 00:17:06,980
you may drink it,

303
00:17:07,340 --> 00:17:08,660
like I’m with you

304
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:10,020
on your wedding.

305
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:14,180
You are so kind to me.

306
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:16,340
I don’t know how to repay you.

307
00:17:17,740 --> 00:17:18,660
Silly girl.

308
00:17:20,580 --> 00:17:23,780
These years, I taught you to read and write poems.

309
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:25,580
We learned to make perfume,

310
00:17:25,820 --> 00:17:27,180
and studied medical science together.

311
00:17:27,620 --> 00:17:28,340
It made me

312
00:17:28,340 --> 00:17:29,540
not feel bored.

313
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:33,300
I don’t want you to leave either.

314
00:17:34,820 --> 00:17:35,700
But

315
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:37,140
you will marry

316
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:38,580
your Mr. right

317
00:17:39,020 --> 00:17:39,820
who waits for you

318
00:17:39,820 --> 00:17:41,340
for tens of hundreds of days.

319
00:17:42,340 --> 00:17:43,380
I’m so happy for you.

320
00:17:48,380 --> 00:17:49,140
Your Majesty.

321
00:18:05,580 --> 00:18:06,380
Your Majesty.

322
00:18:09,100 --> 00:18:10,020
Only this calligraphy work

323
00:18:11,140 --> 00:18:12,180
is changed.

324
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:18,340
The Fan Zhongyan’s work:

325
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:20,460
‘When your learning is as vast as sea,

326
00:18:20,740 --> 00:18:23,220
you’ll have the whole world in your chest.

327
00:18:24,220 --> 00:18:25,380
The wording will be sharp naturally,

328
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:29,100
like the cloud and jades are in your control.’

329
00:18:29,420 --> 00:18:30,700
That is more magnificent.

330
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:38,700
Youheng wrote a letter days ago,

331
00:18:39,460 --> 00:18:40,940
attached with Su Zimei’s new work.

332
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:43,220
I read some sentences and got touched.

333
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:45,300
So I wrote it down and framed it

334
00:18:45,700 --> 00:18:46,740
to replace the old one.

335
00:18:49,580 --> 00:18:51,540
I discussed with Chen Zhizhong two days ago.

336
00:18:52,140 --> 00:18:53,700
Sun Shunqin’s wrongdoing

337
00:18:53,940 --> 00:18:55,620
isn’t a felony about loyalty or filial duty.

338
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:57,140
Demotion to be a civilian

339
00:18:57,620 --> 00:18:58,740
is already a severe punishment.

340
00:18:59,540 --> 00:19:03,180
He may be reinstated to the governor of Huzhou.

341
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:06,940
In terms of politics,

342
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:08,820
you must have thought twice

343
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,620
before making a decision.

344
00:19:14,260 --> 00:19:16,660
But Mrs. Su, Du Youheng, is my best friend.

345
00:19:17,420 --> 00:19:18,860
If Su Shunqin can be reinstated,

346
00:19:19,180 --> 00:19:20,500
I feel happy for her.

347
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:24,180
Thanks for your generosity, Your Majesty.

348
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:31,260
Your Majesty. Would you like to have a drink?

349
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:33,180
It’s new wine made by Her Highness.

350
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:35,140
We also bought jerky, dates,

351
00:19:35,140 --> 00:19:37,100
and golden plum

352
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:38,420
as snacks.

353
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:41,740
OK.

354
00:19:42,100 --> 00:19:43,020
It’s been a long time

355
00:19:43,020 --> 00:19:44,220
since I drank the wine made by Her Highness.

356
00:19:58,300 --> 00:20:00,580
The light yellow suits you the best.

357
00:20:03,220 --> 00:20:06,700
There were new styles in the market last month.

358
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:11,140
I made a new outfit for you.

359
00:20:12,540 --> 00:20:13,900
You’ll love it.

360
00:20:34,780 --> 00:20:35,540
Aunt.

361
00:20:36,900 --> 00:20:37,980
What are you looking at?

362
00:20:44,020 --> 00:20:45,020
Two wild cats

363
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:46,820
were fighting for food,

364
00:20:48,100 --> 00:20:49,100
I drove them away.

365
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:53,260
Aunt.

366
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,500
Did you see

367
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:56,540
something ominous?

368
00:20:58,780 --> 00:20:59,780
I feel like

369
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:03,380
my chamber is cursed.

370
00:21:04,020 --> 00:21:04,740
Chuyue.

371
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:05,820
Yaoyao.

372
00:21:06,700 --> 00:21:07,460
Youwu.

373
00:21:08,580 --> 00:21:09,540
All of them...

374
00:21:09,540 --> 00:21:12,860
Pah. Don’t talk nonsense.

375
00:21:13,340 --> 00:21:14,540
We’ve had a master

376
00:21:14,580 --> 00:21:15,460
to do the rituals.

377
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:16,740
It will be fine.

378
00:21:17,700 --> 00:21:18,740
It’s too windy here.

379
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:20,060
Get in. Don’t catch a cold.

380
00:21:27,220 --> 00:21:28,420
Don’t you make the wine Moyao?

381
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:31,900
I haven’t made wine for long.

382
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:36,220
Qiuhe will get married.

383
00:21:36,740 --> 00:21:37,700
I made the wine

384
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:38,740
for her.

385
00:21:42,060 --> 00:21:42,940
Peach Blossom.

386
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:48,900
The peach blossoms are so beautiful.

387
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:54,540
The bride will make the family happy.

388
00:21:55,460 --> 00:21:57,660
The peach leaves are lush.

389
00:21:58,060 --> 00:22:01,660
The bride will make the family harmonious.

390
00:22:04,420 --> 00:22:05,740
Did you also

391
00:22:06,020 --> 00:22:07,340
make Peach Blossom before you got married?

392
00:22:10,820 --> 00:22:11,860
Before I got married?

393
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:18,460
It’s been too long.

394
00:22:19,020 --> 00:22:20,340
I’ve forgot it.

395
00:22:27,060 --> 00:22:27,900
Yeah.

396
00:22:30,100 --> 00:22:31,780
It’s already the time

397
00:22:31,780 --> 00:22:33,500
to pick groom-to-be for Huirou.

398
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:38,300
I discussed with the officials

399
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:40,140
about Huirou’s marriage today.

400
00:22:40,340 --> 00:22:41,540
I recommended Li Wei.

401
00:22:42,340 --> 00:22:44,380
Officials used to be divided into two factions.

402
00:22:44,940 --> 00:22:46,980
One faction agrees, while the other objects.

403
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:49,180
Or both factions object,

404
00:22:50,740 --> 00:22:52,300
never like what happened today

405
00:22:53,420 --> 00:22:57,060
that all officials called it’s wise of His Majesty,

406
00:22:59,700 --> 00:23:01,060
as if their emperor

407
00:23:02,060 --> 00:23:03,300
did something right

408
00:23:03,820 --> 00:23:05,620
finally.

409
00:23:13,340 --> 00:23:14,380
Li Wei is a good match

410
00:23:16,740 --> 00:23:18,820
for Huirou.

411
00:23:21,420 --> 00:23:22,260
How so?

412
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:12,540
Part of the painting

413
00:24:12,620 --> 00:24:14,140
is made by Li Wei.

414
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:19,300
Part of it is on the handkerchief originally.

415
00:24:20,860 --> 00:24:22,580
From the part painted by Li Wei,

416
00:24:23,740 --> 00:24:26,620
like the flying bird and reeds,

417
00:24:27,500 --> 00:24:29,620
obviously he painted

418
00:24:29,900 --> 00:24:30,900
on a whim.

419
00:24:32,940 --> 00:24:34,420
Did he give these to you?

420
00:24:36,940 --> 00:24:38,060
No. He came to the palace

421
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:40,500
with his father for banquets before.

422
00:24:41,460 --> 00:24:43,060
He didn’t get a chance to see Huirou,

423
00:24:43,820 --> 00:24:45,940
or he was too nervous to see her.

424
00:24:46,340 --> 00:24:48,900
So, he asked someone to send

425
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:50,540
Huirou’s favorite cakes, dried fruits, sweetmeats

426
00:24:50,620 --> 00:24:51,620
to me

427
00:24:51,940 --> 00:24:52,980
to give them to Huirou.

428
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:55,180
These are

429
00:24:55,180 --> 00:24:57,180
silk handkerchiefs wrapping the snacks.

430
00:25:04,500 --> 00:25:06,140
The pattern painted with light-colored ink

431
00:25:06,460 --> 00:25:08,100
isn’t integrated with the original pattern

432
00:25:08,860 --> 00:25:09,780
on the handkerchief.

433
00:25:10,940 --> 00:25:12,300
They are not coordinated.

434
00:25:12,740 --> 00:25:14,540
So, it isn’t painted on purpose.

435
00:25:16,260 --> 00:25:17,260
But these two strokes

436
00:25:18,820 --> 00:25:19,900
are graceful and flexible.

437
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:22,700
They are vividly portrayed.

438
00:25:24,780 --> 00:25:25,540
After that,

439
00:25:26,820 --> 00:25:28,020
I paid attention to him.

440
00:25:29,420 --> 00:25:30,460
At the banquets,

441
00:25:31,260 --> 00:25:32,420
he was neither interested in the shows,

442
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:36,020
nor did he try to befriend the nobles.

443
00:25:37,220 --> 00:25:39,340
He just bowed his head

444
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:41,980
and drew with wine on the desk.

445
00:25:43,220 --> 00:25:44,380
Li Wei painted,

446
00:25:46,020 --> 00:25:47,580
because the painting was in his heart.

447
00:25:47,620 --> 00:25:48,740
Due to the feelings in his heart,

448
00:25:48,860 --> 00:25:50,100
the painting was made.

449
00:25:50,860 --> 00:25:52,060
Neither told others

450
00:25:52,740 --> 00:25:54,660
nor left it to himself.

451
00:25:55,460 --> 00:25:57,820
It’s all what he saw and what he felt.

452
00:25:59,900 --> 00:26:01,380
Li Wei loves Huirou,

453
00:26:02,820 --> 00:26:04,780
because he thinks Huirou is lovely.

454
00:26:06,340 --> 00:26:07,660
He wants to be good to Huirou

455
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:09,380
and get close to her.

456
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:12,020
He doesn’t even think about

457
00:26:12,260 --> 00:26:14,060
how to make Huirou love him.

458
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:18,220
As for the glory Huirou can bring him,

459
00:26:18,620 --> 00:26:21,060
it’s beyond his expectation.

460
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,700
The officials have their own reason

461
00:26:25,260 --> 00:26:28,380
to agree on the marriage.

462
00:26:28,900 --> 00:26:31,100
You have your reason, too.

463
00:26:31,620 --> 00:26:34,820
This is just my personal opinion.

464
00:26:38,140 --> 00:26:39,660
I still remember

465
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,460
the moment all the officials praised:

466
00:26:41,460 --> 00:26:42,940
it’s wise of Your Majesty.

467
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:49,260
When?

468
00:26:52,460 --> 00:26:54,180
When I chose you to be the Empress.

469
00:27:01,780 --> 00:27:04,420
The reason why the officials chose Li Wei

470
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:08,340
is the same as the one

471
00:27:11,140 --> 00:27:13,340
that they chose me.

472
00:27:15,060 --> 00:27:17,820
We are unable to bewitch the Emperor

473
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,420
and interfere with the politics.

474
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:22,380
For the ladies accompanying the Emperor,

475
00:27:23,060 --> 00:27:25,700
their beauty is a flaw.

476
00:27:26,780 --> 00:27:28,180
For the men assisting the Emperor,

477
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:30,180
their talent is a taboo.

478
00:27:31,180 --> 00:27:32,100
They also share

479
00:27:32,100 --> 00:27:33,500
common reasons to agree,

480
00:27:34,460 --> 00:27:35,660
the family background and characters.

481
00:27:38,620 --> 00:27:40,060
But they were misled

482
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:40,940
by the rumors

483
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:42,540
about Danshu’s beauty,

484
00:27:45,220 --> 00:27:46,580
and also

485
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:48,380
Li Wei’s unknown talent.

486
00:27:49,980 --> 00:27:50,940
Actually,

487
00:27:53,020 --> 00:27:55,100
I was grateful for the rumors back then.

488
00:28:08,660 --> 00:28:09,580
But

489
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:12,820
you’re contented with the choice of empress

490
00:28:13,340 --> 00:28:14,420
for the sake of country.

491
00:28:18,460 --> 00:28:19,300
However,

492
00:28:21,420 --> 00:28:23,060
Huirou is reluctant

493
00:28:24,980 --> 00:28:26,220
to get married for the country.

494
00:28:27,740 --> 00:28:28,460
No.

495
00:28:29,420 --> 00:28:30,220
Not like that.

496
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:34,700
Your Majesty picked the empress for the country,

497
00:28:35,980 --> 00:28:37,900
but definitely not betroths her for that reason.

498
00:28:39,580 --> 00:28:41,620
Can Huirou see Li Wei’s talent

499
00:28:42,300 --> 00:28:44,500
and his sincerity

500
00:28:45,060 --> 00:28:46,740
through his clumsiness

501
00:28:46,740 --> 00:28:47,860
and slow speech?

502
00:28:50,540 --> 00:28:51,820
In Huirou’s mind,

503
00:28:52,860 --> 00:28:54,540
you didn’t consider her feelings at all

504
00:28:56,660 --> 00:28:58,380
before making the decision.

505
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:11,820
Li Wei will love her heart and soul,

506
00:29:13,380 --> 00:29:15,260
without secular suspicions,

507
00:29:16,580 --> 00:29:19,180
jealousy, and calculation.

508
00:29:21,060 --> 00:29:23,020
Have you ever loved me like that?

509
00:30:01,940 --> 00:30:03,140
You married me.

510
00:30:07,060 --> 00:30:09,020
Wasn’t it because you had no choice?

511
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:15,180
Was it your own wish

512
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:17,900
to marry me

513
00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:19,900
as your wife?

514
00:30:25,900 --> 00:30:26,700
Back then...

515
00:30:28,540 --> 00:30:29,580
-I...
-After that,

516
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,860
weren’t you

517
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:40,580
cold to me for years?

518
00:30:45,780 --> 00:30:47,500
You treated me that way.

519
00:30:49,660 --> 00:30:51,220
Should I

520
00:30:52,140 --> 00:30:55,100
beg you for favor?

521
00:31:00,860 --> 00:31:04,340
Is it that you calculated

522
00:31:05,060 --> 00:31:09,460
or I was suspicious?

523
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:32,940
What the heck is the Peach Blossom?

524
00:31:33,860 --> 00:31:34,860
It’s sour and bitter.

525
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:37,140
Not wonderful

526
00:31:37,140 --> 00:31:37,980
like beautiful blossoms.

527
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:40,460
Neither the thickness of the fruits.

528
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:41,580
Not to mention

529
00:31:41,940 --> 00:31:43,660
the strong flavor of the lush leaves.

530
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:55,060
That’s right.

531
00:31:57,820 --> 00:32:01,900
My wine has no strong flavor of lush leaves.

532
00:32:08,220 --> 00:32:08,980
Qiuhe.

533
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,540
Qiuhe, get the lantern ready.

534
00:32:15,380 --> 00:32:16,420
Call Liaozi here

535
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:17,940
to pick up His Majesty.

536
00:32:18,540 --> 00:32:19,500
I don’t leave.

537
00:32:26,260 --> 00:32:27,820
Even if it’s for the country,

538
00:32:28,620 --> 00:32:30,180
you’re still my wife.

539
00:32:32,260 --> 00:32:34,340
I’ve indulged you for 15 years.

540
00:32:36,020 --> 00:32:36,660
Enough!

541
00:32:39,180 --> 00:32:39,980
What are you doing?

542
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:42,420
Are you going to hurt me?

543
00:32:47,020 --> 00:32:49,060
You want to apologize again?

544
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:09,060
Sorry.

545
00:33:43,580 --> 00:33:45,420
Aunt. Tonight, should we...

546
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,620
Stay right here.

547
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:52,300
Don’t try to do anything stupid.

548
00:33:55,900 --> 00:33:56,740
Let me tell you.

549
00:33:57,860 --> 00:33:59,620
If you can give birth to a prince,

550
00:33:59,940 --> 00:34:01,660
you’ll get both glory and wealth.

551
00:34:02,180 --> 00:34:02,940
But you have to

552
00:34:02,940 --> 00:34:03,980
remember this.

553
00:34:04,300 --> 00:34:05,780
Bihan is your senior forever.

554
00:34:06,420 --> 00:34:07,380
Don’t try to surpass her.

555
00:34:08,100 --> 00:34:10,260
His Majesty won’t allow you either.

556
00:36:34,890 --> 00:36:36,166
Fire!

557
00:36:36,660 --> 00:36:37,500
-Fire!
-Your Majesty.

558
00:36:46,220 --> 00:36:47,220
Fire!

559
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:48,956
-Help!
-Go get water!

560
00:36:49,140 --> 00:36:50,060
-Help!
-Go get water!

561
00:36:50,220 --> 00:36:51,660
Fire!

562
00:36:51,660 --> 00:36:52,780
Hurry. Fire!

563
00:36:52,780 --> 00:36:54,460
Tell others there’s a fire.

564
00:36:54,620 --> 00:36:55,260
Fire!

565
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:56,100
Hurry. Hurry.

566
00:36:56,135 --> 00:36:57,453
-Fire!
-Fire!

567
00:36:57,500 --> 00:36:58,340
Hurry.

568
00:37:06,820 --> 00:37:07,700
What’s happening?

569
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:10,300
What’s going on?

